```
<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background: #f5f0ff;
        color: #2d2340;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 370px;
        background: white;
        padding: 40px 35px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(109, 76, 175, 0.08);
    }

    .logo {
        width: 65px;
        height: 65px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #7653b8;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: white;
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #6d4caf;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    p {
        text-align: center;
        color: #8b8099;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .input-box {
        margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .input-box label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #4a3b5c;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .input-box input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        border: 1px solid #d9ccef;
        border-radius: 7px;
        outline: none;
        transition: 0.2s;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #2d2340;
    }

    .input-box input::placeholder {
        color: #9d91ad;
    }

    .input-box input:focus {
        border-color: #8b6bc5;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(139, 107, 197, 0.1);
    }

    .forgot {
        text-align: right;
        margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .forgot a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #7653b8;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .forgot a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    button {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 7px;
        background: #7c5cbf;
        color: white;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.2s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background: #6849a8;
    }

    .signup {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 22px;
        color: #756b80;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .signup a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #7653b8;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .signup a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 450px) {
        .container {
            padding: 35px 25px;
        }
    }
</style>
```

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

```
<div class="logo">
    🔗
</div>

<h1>Welcome Back</h1>

<p>Login to manage your shortened URLs</p>

<form action="/user/login" method="post">

    <div class="input-box">
        <label>Email</label>

        <input
            name="email"
            type="email"
            placeholder="Enter your email"
            required
        >
    </div>

    <div class="input-box">
        <label>Password</label>

        <input
            name="password"
            type="password"
            placeholder="Enter your password"
            required
        >
    </div>

    <div class="forgot">
        <a href="#">Forgot Password?</a>
    </div>

    <button type="submit">
        Login
    </button>

</form>

<div class="signup">
    Don't have an account?
    <a href="/user/signup">Create Account</a>
</div>
```

</div>

</body>
